 some important countries like Germany, and the company is</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/505524402/image_505524402.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741991-nomad-foods-had-a-good-3q24-but-im-less-attracted-to-the-companys-prospects", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 12:56:21"}, {"id": "4741990", "title": "BRW: Strong Recent Performance Has Improved This Fund", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Hand holding American currency\" data-id=\"145671149\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1176px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Anthony Bradshaw</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The <strong>Saba Capital Income &amp; Opportu