static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253986380/image_1253986380.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Main Thesis and Background</h2> <p>The purpose of this article is to evaluate the Vanguard FTSE Emerging Markets ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VWO\" title=\"Vanguard FTSE Emerging Markets Index Fund ETF Shares\">VWO</a></span>) as an investment option. The fund is managed by Vanguard and its <a href=\"https://investor.vanguard.com/etf/profile/VWO\" rel=\"nofollow\">objective</a> is to \"invest in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253986380/image_1253986380.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741988-vwo-emerging-markets-face-a-slew-of-risks-in-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 12:43:48"}, {"id": "4741985", "title": "Hafnia Limited: $100 Million Reason To Hold Your Nose And Stick With The Clean Product Trade", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Stock buyback and Share buybacks is shown using the text\" data-id=\"1912124068\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Andrii Dodonov</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p>In September, I wrote two very bullish pieces on the clean product trade for both TORM plc (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TRMD\" title=\"TORM plc\">TRMD</a>) and Hafnia Limited (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HAFN\" title=\"Hafnia Limited\">HAFN</a></span>). <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4723741-hafnia-limited-a-20-percent-yield-and-the-best-value-on-the-water\">The gist of those articles centered around the continued polarization</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741985-hafnia-limited-100-million-reason-to-hold-your-nose-and-stick-with-the-clean-product-trade", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 12:33:22"}, {"id": "4741980", "title": "Vertical Aerospace: Rally Is A Good Selling Opportunity", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Conceptual eVTOL (electric vertical take-off and landing) aircrafts as a taxi/shuttle service at the helipad on top of a building\" data-id=\"1394967815\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">adventtr</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Initiating Coverage</h2> <p>eVTOL or flying car stocks have been surging higher in the recent past. Some of the notable names in the industry at a nascent stage includes Archer Aviation (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ACHR\" title=\"Archer Aviation Inc.\">ACHR</a>) and Joby Aviation (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/JOBY\" title=\"Joby Aviation, Inc.\">JOBY</a>). While</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741980-vertical-aerospace-rally-is-a-good-selling-opportunity", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 12:25:29"}, {"id": "4741994", "title": "Underlying Job Market Dynamics Begin To Retighten; Fed Backpedaling On Pace And Depth Of Rate Cuts", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businesspeople carrying boxes around on painted lanes on asphalt\" data-id=\"912016096\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The underlying dynamics of the labor market bounced back in October, according to the Job Openings and Labor Turnover Survey (JOLTS) from the Bureau of Labor Statistics on Tuesday. The data continues to be muddled by the Boeing strike that lasted through</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741994-underlying-job-market-dynamics-retightening-fed-backpedaling-on-pace-depth-of-rate-cuts", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 12:20:00"}, {"id": "4741979", "title": "SHY: Short Duration Is In Again", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1708218794/image_1708218794.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Silhouette of Bank symbol and Percentage model on wood table. Concepts of the banking system, rising interest rates, inflation, deflation, and savings.\" data-id=\"1708218794\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1708218794/image_1708218794.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1708218794/image_1708218794.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1708218794/image_1708218794.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1708218794/image_1708218794.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1708218794/image_1708218794.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1708218794/image_1708218794.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1708218794/image_1708218794.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1708218794/image_1708218794.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">sommart</p></figcapt